**Business logic from `electric_rate.jsp`:**
- `GET /api/v1/electric-rates` â†’ List all rates ordered by ID
- `POST /api/v1/electric-rates` â†’ Bulk insert 4 tariff categories for a month (`0-100`, `101-300`, `301-500`, `>500`). Reject if rates already exist for the month.
